<p>What is the other proper way to do this JavaFx with Scene builder? </p>  <pre><code>TIA Warning message : javafx controller must have 0 or exactly 1 argument </code></pre>  <p>Code:</p>  <pre><code>private ObservableList&lt;String&gt; msg = FXCollections.observableArrayList("Msg","Msg");  @FXML private void sendMessage(ActionEvent event, String messageBody) {     if(message.getText().equals("")){         System.out.println("Nothing");     }     else{         String username = "Blue : ";         msg.add(username + messageBody);         message.clear();         box.scrollTo(Integer.MAX_VALUE);     } } </code></pre>